Modification Version: 15.0.0.0.1 Date: 25-Mar-2024
Bug 36434781 -> Changes for RowType_IFW_PRICEMDL_STEP on LoadIfwConfig.xsd
Problem:
----------
THRESHOLD_FROM and THRESHOLD_TO of pipeline IFW_PRICEMDL_STEP table 
supports upto 15 digit decimal only.
Solution
----------
The THRESHOLD_FROM and THRESHOLD_TO of IFW_PRICEMDL_STEP is now modified to 
support upto 28 digit as pipeline supports upto 28 digit decimal when 
MAX28DIGIT_DECIMAL_SUPPORT=Y is enabled.
