Bug 35607183 -> LoadIfwConfig utility is failing
Problem:
----------
The LoadIfwConfig utility is failing to load and core is generated.
Solution
----------
The missing return statement in a non void method was causing
issue due to compiler optimization in latest compiler. Added default
return statement to fix the issue.
